column4: China regulator queries Microsoft on findings in anti-trust probe
column5: SHANGHAI China's industry and commerce regulator has asked Microsoft Corp to explain "major issues" that it says have come to light from digital data obtained as part of an anti-trust investigation.

column4: Nvidia says Volvo is first customer for new autonomous drive computer
column5: LAS VEGAS Nvidia Corp. unveiled a new  lunchbox-size super-computer for self-driving cars and said Volvo Car Group will be the new device's first customer.
